|               |   Sort: u DESC NULLS FIRST                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
|               |     Projection: hits.MobilePhone, hits.MobilePhoneModel, count(DISTINCT hits.UserID) AS u                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |       Aggregate: groupBy=[[hits.MobilePhone, hits.MobilePhoneModel]], aggr=[[count(DISTINCT hits.UserID)]]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
